OL,3,CLondon's Night Czar to quit the
OL,4,C#130,000-a-year role
OL,6,FShe first took on the role in 2016
OL,7,Fwith a brief to champion all aspects
OL,8,Fof London's life at night, including
OL,9,Fsupporting under threat venues,
OL,10,Fimprove women's safety and stand up
OL,11,Ffor the capital's 1.3m night workers.
OL,13,FEmma Best, Chair of the GLA Oversight
OL,14,FCommittee claimed the role of Night
OL,15,FCzar had been a 'complete waste of
OL,16,Finvestment' in the night time industry.
OL,18,FThe Mayor of London, Sadiq Khan, said:
OL,19,F"I'd like to thank Amy for everything
OL,20,Fthat she's done as the capital's first-
OL,21,Fever Night Czar.
