OL,3,CLondon's Night Czar to quit the
OL,4,C#130,000-a-year role
OL,6,F"Cities across the UK and the world
OL,7,Fhave created their own champions for
OL,8,Flife at night in recent years, and
OL,9,Fit's been inspiring to work alongside
OL,10,Fthem.
OL,12,F"Despite the ongoing challenges that
OL,13,Fit faces, I know that London's life at
OL,14,Fnight will continue to evolve and I
OL,15,Flook forward to seeing the work that
OL,16,Fhas already started to deliver the
OL,17,FMayor's manifesto pledges, as I begin
OL,18,Fmy next chapter."
